{"type":"click","text":"A\n    \n      Auto-Open & Live Update\n      When the AI creates or modifies a file, it automatically opens as a tab in the editor and the content updates in real-time. The editor auto-switches to the file being modified. User sees the AI \"typing\" code live.\n      \n        \n          \n            🤖\n            AI writes\n          \n          →\n          \n            \n              page.tsx ●\n            \n            \n              export default Home() {\n              return (\n              <h1>Welcome</h1> ◀ just written\n            \n          \n          →\n          \n            🌐\n            Preview updates\n          \n        \n      \n      \n        ProsUser sees exactly what AI is doingFeels magical — like pair programmingBuilds trust and transparency\n        ConsCan be distracting if AI edits many files fastEditor may flicker during rapid changes","choice":"a","id":null,"timestamp":1773621293012}
